  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA28">
<l>pūṇāka voṉṟu puṉaintoṉṟu poṅkataḷi</l>
<l>ṉāṇāka mēṉmiḷira naṉkamaittuk - kōṇākam</l>
<l>poṉmuṭimēṟ cūṭuvatu mellām poṟiyiliyēṟ</l>
<l>keṉmuṭiva tāka vivar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being decorated with one piece of ondulating skin as an ornament,</l>
<l>well appointing a murderous snake so that it turns as a thread,</l>
<l>all [that] he wears on [his] golden crown/knot. What is he</l>
<l>as an accomplishment for me?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
